{"tid":1199583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"探討外國示威者推進的方式","createTime":"2019-06-10T14:01:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T14:01:25.000Z","uid":28393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"74c9fbe0695052c45c5402fd68e1880069995fae","tid":1199583,"uid":28393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:01:25.000Z","msg":"引用巴打搵到的YouTube link，發覺大部分都係:<br />\n1. 製造煙幕，用火攻，令能見度降低。一來可以提供掩護，二來阻礙對方前進路線<br />\n2. 近身攻擊使用長棍或障礙物，保持和對方距離，方便前進和後退<br />\n3. 投擲物，遠距離控制對方，讓對方不得前進，為近身進攻佈局或掩護撤退<br />\n4. 應付盾牌的方法，應該以破壞對方視野為主，投擲可黏附在盾牌上得顏料或麵粉類，或淋佢一身紅油<br />\n5. 大部分情況都係10-20人一組，游擊式前進或撤退，所以對現場環境需要有充分了解，不能被對方慢慢收窄範圍，最後只能坐以待斃<br />\n6. 近身攻擊大部分係對付2-3個，如果對方係一個小隊，都係遠攻為主。<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家睇完仲有冇其他意見呢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LZecI195bvQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLZecI195bvQ&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3Xtw8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=38de64d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LZecI195bvQ</a><br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hor_hJqNoS0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dhor_hJqNoS0&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3Xtw8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=937989b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hor_hJqNoS0</a><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rtlaOekIQbU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrtlaOekIQbU&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3Xtw8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=1bd2f7b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rtlaOekIQbU</a>"}]}